org.springframework.core.io.ProtocolResolver

  • 使用ProtocolResolver的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    org.springframework.context
    This package builds on the beans package to add support for message sources and for the Observer design pattern, and the ability for application objects to obtain resources using a consistent API.
    org.springframework.core.io
    Generic abstraction for (file-based) resources, used throughout the framework.

    • org.springframework.context中ProtocolResolver的使用

      参数类型为ProtocolResolver的org.springframework.context中的方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      void ConfigurableApplicationContext.addProtocolResolver(ProtocolResolver resolver)
      Register the given protocol resolver with this application context, allowing for additional resource protocols to be handled.
